'''Schickele''' was a skill and chance card game usually played for high stakes. Members of the [[Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes/Legends|Modal Nodes]] once played a few hands of Schickele at the [[Lucky Despot]] Hotel & Casino on the eve of the wedding of Lady [[Valarian/Legends|Valarian]] and [[D'Wopp]].

